      .col-md-12 
        p The Iron Yard is the umbrella for a national, multi-campus design and development school. It is vital that the Shield Mark be consistent throughout any collateral that is produced-print and digital. These rules are meant to be a framework in which to guide designers and developers on the acceptable ways to communicate using The Iron Yard's brand language. We're not saying that we're not flexible, but you have to know the rules before you can break them.
      
