      .col-md-12  
        p The main typeface that is used throughout The Iron Yard's collateral is Tisa Pro. Flimotype and Gravity are also used, but they are reserved for the construction of the Shield Mark. Tisa Pro Medium is mainly used for headlines and Tisa Pro Regular is used for body copy. The Medium font can be used for body copy as well. Tisa Pro Bold is mainly used for call to action text, or smaller text that needs to attract the viewer's attention. It works very well when displayed in all caps. Using any of the fonts in italics is another useful way to emphasize a word or phrase. The website uses the same typeface with a slightly different an more specific set of rules. They can be found <a href="http://masondesu.github.io/ghost-shield/">here</a>.
